19.title: Skibidi War   Toilets Attack
19.description: Welcome to Skibidi War, a one-of-a-kind strategy shooter game set in the heart of Skibidi Toilet City. Here, the Skibidi Toilets face off against the innovative Camera Heads in a rousing war. Think youve experienced all shooter defense games? Skibidi war will redefine your expectations. Survive and defend your territory from a ceaseless attack of these dangerous rivals in a game that humorously mingles the epic with the everyday.
19.instructions: You need to control the toilet to run continuously and defeat other toilets to win You can also pick up some weapons and use them to strengthen yourself
